$LNG['CONDITION_66']			= 'Antaris Legacy uses Google Analytics, a web analytics service provided by Google Inc. (Google).<br /><br />        Google Analytics uses cookies, which are text files placed on your computer to help the website analyze site usage by its users.       The data generated by the cookie about your use of the website (including your IP address) is transmitted and stored by Google on servers in the United States.<br /><br />              Google will use this information to evaluate your use of the website, compiling reports on website activity to Antaris Legacy and providing other services relating to website activity and Internet use.<br /><br />              Google may also transfer this information to third parties where required by law or where such third parties process the information on Google behalf, including in particular the editor of this site. Google will not cut your IP address with other Google data.<br /><br />        You can disable the use of cookies by selecting the appropriate settings on your browser. However, this deactivation could prevent the use of some features of this website.       Using Antaris Legacy platforms, you consent to the processing of data by Google in the manner and for the purposes described above.';
$LNG['CONDITION_67']			= 'Your personal data will naturally not be sold to third parties. However, Antaris Legacy transmit to third parties personal data provided by you, besides the use of Google Analytics, only in the following cases : Payment service providers (PayPal, AlloPass), host (OVH). These service providers have access to your personal data in the limit allowing them to perform their tasks.       These providers are required to process your personal data in accordance with this declaration of personal data protection and the basic laws governing data protection.';
