$LNG['CONDITION_69']			= 'In general, without the written permission of the company, it is prohibited to contract with a third party any agreement on the transfer, use or storage of personal data or accounts. So it is particularly prohibited to sell accounts or resources (or other component of an account) or to make a profit by leaving accounts (or one of its components) in favor of a third party :       indeed, it is still owned by Antaris Legacy and therefore can not make the object of an transaction.<br /><br />        The same prohibitions apply to personal data and rights of use.       Is particularly relevant here, any transaction against Allopass, or anything of value.<br /><br />        Violation of these rules or any other right of society, particularly those concerning copyrights, will be forwarded to the authorities and confirmed by civil and/or criminal. Additional penalties may also be taken by the company, including the blocking of all the offending user accounts.';
